Powerful scene editor with a focus on performance and optimization for mobile games.
Written in JavaScript or TypeScript for rapid prototyping and web compatibility.
Designed for 2D games but supports lightweight 3D games as well.
Easy integration with third-party services like analytics, ads, and in-app purchases.
Strong focus on mobile performance and small build sizes.
Integrated asset management for sprites, textures, and sounds.

Website: https://www.cocos.com/en/creator
